        "rich_text_9hwRAc": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Heading",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h1>Ring Shapes and Cuts</h1>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "follow_us_ygY8aG": {
          "type": "follow_us",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Follow Us on"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ccxpK9": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Ring shopping can be overwhelming, especially when there are so many diamond shapes and cuts for you to choose the perfect one. Rings that are made out of precious metals such as gold and platinum are designed for milestone moments - to mark the moments with something just as grand as the moment. If you are looking for a guide to help you through the different types of ring shapes and cuts, you have come to the right place. At Lucira Jewelry, our entire collection is lab grown diamond certified. Our grown diamond ring shapes and cuts are crafted to last forever, each having its own beauty. This guide covers everything you need to know about cuts and shapes, from the types to who they are ideal for. e content here...</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_kKqW7n": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": " Shape & Diamond Cut",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Understanding the Difference Between Diamond Shape & Diamond Cuts</h2>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_KhakP7": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Shapes_Cut_16_9.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_kcy6qD": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": " Shape & Diamond Cut P1",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>It is common to get confused between a diamond’s shape and cut, but they are different. Diamond shapes mean the external outline, such as round, oval, pear, square or any silhouette that determines the shape of the diamond. Diamond cuts, on the other side, mean the proportions and the finish of the diamond, such as bezel or emerald. The diamond shape and cut determine the overall look of the diamond, including the way it reflects light and shines. Essentially speaking, a diamond shape is the shape of the ring that you see from above, and a diamond cut is the way you see the diamond sign. Apart from the popular shapes and cuts, a lab grown diamond ring comes with different options in both shapes and cuts, letting you customize the look the way you wish! </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BxFmqg": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Exploring Diamond Shapes",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Exploring Diamond Shapes</h2><p>Let’s first have a look at the different types of diamond shapes. Cultured diamonds come in a wide range of shapes, making it challenging to choose one. Each diamond shape has its distinct aura, and to decide which one is the most <em>you, </em>we have listed below not only the different shapes, but the kind of look each one provides, and who is that shape ideal for.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_znfWE9": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Round Brilliant",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Round Brilliant - The Timeless Sparklee</h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_AynJ8F": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Round_Brilliant_-_The_Timeless_Sparkle_501b4eb7-1733-4a3a-977e-bf30c14c915a.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Look: </p><p>The round shape is the most classic diamond shape, with symmetrical brilliance and unmatched sparkle. This classic shape is most often preferred for solitaire rings. </p><p>Ideal For: </p><p>Those who value everlasting style, balance, and tradition. Round shaped diamonds are for the ones who appreciate everlasting shine and simplicity that never fades. It complements all hand types. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jbd43L": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Round cut Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Why Choose It:</p><p>The round cut suits all kinds of hands, and elevates all types of outfits from a crisp shirt to an evening gown. Its the ultimate everyday luxury. </p><p>Lucira Tip:</p><p>Although classic with no twists, lab grown diamond jewellery with a round cut looks timeless and reflects the most brilliance, ideal for you if you want a versatile choice. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Ymw3K6": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Princess - The Modern Icon",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Princess - The Modern Icon</h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_zpxzBh": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Princess_-_The_Modern_Icon_02fb6bbe-fcc7-440d-bef0-bf2cf4baa660.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Look:</p><p>A princess shape is essentially a square-shaped diamond with defined corners and intense internal reflections. It is the perfect engagement ring for someone who loves a structured yet minimal design. </p><p>Ideal For:</p><p>A modern and ambitious woman, and someone who is drawn to geometrical designs. It looks stunning on small or slender hands due to its clean, angular silhouette.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ejh96n": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Princess  Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Why Choose It:</p><p>The princess shape exudes strength and gives an edge to the overall personality that radiates because of diamond jewelry. </p><p>Lucira Tip:</p><p>Secure your princess-shaped diamond with a halo or a prong setting to make it ideal for daily wear. Style it with sleek, tailored outfits to create a perfect modern aesthetic look. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_x9FJbV": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Oval - The Effortless Grace ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Oval - The Effortless Grace </h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_VWDmRU": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Oval_-_The_Effortless_Grace.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Look: </p><p>An oval shaped diamond radiates an effortless charm with soft elongated curves that blend brilliance with beauty. </p><p>Ideal For:</p><p>Romantic souls who love understated luxury. An oval shaped diamond is ideal for short or wider fingers as they have a wonderful slimming effect. </p><p></p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BWVmEe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Oval Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Why Choose It:</p><p>Oval diamonds appear larger than their carat weight, offering the perfect balance of sophistication and sparkle.</p><p>Lucira Tip:</p><p>This magical shaped diamond makes your fingers look longer, adding grace to every gesture. Pair it with soft and elegant fabrics such as silk or chiffon to enhance the elegance that radiates.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bPLMNC": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Cushion - The Romantic Glow",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Cushion - The Romantic Glow</h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_zwVAkV": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Cushion_-_The_Romantic_Glow.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Look: </p><p>A cushion ring brings the best of both the worlds - square and round. This cushion ring has a soft and pillow-like look that glows beautifully. </p><p>Ideal For:</p><p>Anyone who loves vintage-inspired design with a touch of modernity. It flatters medium to broad hands due to its soft, rounded shape. Perfect for gifting and milestone moments such as birthdays and anniversaries. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_TbC4mN": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Cushion Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Why Choose It:</p><p>Every facet of a cushion ring enhances the sparkle of the diamond, adding to the charm and luxury of a diamond ring. </p><p>Lucira Tip:</p><p>Pair a cushion lab created diamond engagement ring with a rose gold band sitting on top of it. This will bring out the warmth of the cushion ring and shine even better. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_dEkM3m": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Emerald - The Mirror of Elegance",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Emerald - The Mirror of Elegance</h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NwRy9R": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Emerald_-_The_Mirror_of_Elegance_550c1bdd-deab-469b-92b6-2f585e1ef5ed.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Look: </p><p>An emerald cut is rectangular with long facets, known for its “hall of mirrors” reflections. </p><p>Ideal For:</p><p>For anyone who appreciates timeless architecture, an emerald shaped diamond is the perfect choice. It looks wonderful on long fingers enhancing the symmetry to the overall look. </p><p></p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_jMYfry": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": " Emerald Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Why Choose It:<br/><br/>A lab grown emerald cut diamond looks exceptionally refined and poised. It pairs beautifully with sleek evening dresses and power dressing, looking stunning and speaking volumes while being minimal. </p><p>Lucira Tip:</p><p>Keep polishing the diamond frequently. The clarity of the facets adds to the beauty of the diamond, radiating sophistication and utter awe. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_9Wthqw": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Pear - The Signature Statement",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Pear - The Signature Statement</h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_iiFrKE": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Pear_-_The_Signature_Statement.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Look:</p><p>A pear cut diamond is a teardrop silhouette that blends the brilliance of a round with the uniqueness of a marquise.</p><p>Ideal For:</p><p>Artistic and adventurous personalities love a pear-shaped diamond for it stands out in a crowd. A pear diamond is usually the go-to choice for small hands or short fingers, as it creates an illusion of an elongated look. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_UDAiej": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Pear Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Why Choose It:</p><p>A pear shaped diamond gives an elongated and unique look, blending the brilliance of a classic round diamond with a modern look with a teardrop look.</p><p>Lucira Tip:</p><p>Wear the pointed look upwards to create an elongated look, elevating the overall charismatic look. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_CbXLkg": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Marquise - The Regal Silhouette",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Marquise - The Regal Silhouette</h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NiGrXL": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Marquise_-_The_Regal_Silhouette.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Look:</p><p>A marquise diamond has pointed outwards on both the sides, offering a dramatic visual length. </p><p>Ideal For:</p><p>Bold, statement-loving personalities. This is a kind of ring that completes the look - especially couture-inspired outfits meant to look exclusive and daring. </p><p><br/></p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_tdEjrE": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Marquise Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Why Choose It:</p><p>It is a stunning choice to create impact as the elongated shape maximizes carat appearance. </p><p>Lucira Tip:</p><p>Choose a marquise diamond when you want to upgrade to a bigger-looking size, without paying an increased cvd diamond price for more carat weight as a marquise diamond looks larger for its carat weight. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_hEAXhx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Exploring Diamond Cuts",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Exploring Diamond Cuts</h2><p>A diamond cut is meant to interact with light, creating allure and adding depth to the ring for an enhanced look. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7Tbwbe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Bezel Cut - The Modern Minimalist",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Bezel Cut - The Modern Minimalist</h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NN3FF4": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Bezel_Cut_-_The_Modern_Minimalist.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Look:</p><p>A smooth rim frames the diamond, offering protection and clean edges to the diamond. </p><p>Ideal For:</p><p>An active lifestyle. A bezel cut is a sportsperson’s best friend and is perfect for women who are occupied with physical activities or travel a lot. One can be carefree about the diamond even when you are clumsy or occupied with work, with this diamond cut. </p><p></p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        }
      },
